time and participation

00:38:30.690 --> 00:38:33.450
in that system and your
experience of then being

00:38:33.450 --> 00:38:36.487
so publicly rejected from it?

00:38:36.487 --> 00:38:38.070
GRETCHEN CARLSON:
Well, what I can say

00:38:38.070 --> 00:38:42.180
is that, to a certain
extent, all people

00:38:42.180 --> 00:38:44.730
