00:38:44.730 --> 00:38:48.570
I've always been a
supporter of women, always.

00:38:48.570 --> 00:38:49.320
Call my mom up.

00:38:49.320 --> 00:38:52.620
She used to get so bugged by me
calling her early in my career

00:38:52.620 --> 00:38:55.760
and throughout and saying, women
aren't paid fairly, et cetera.

00:38:55.760 --> 00:38:57.260
And she'd be like,
why do you always

00:38:57.260 --> 00:38:58.926
have to talk about
women's rights stuff?

00:38:58.926 --> 00:39:00.960
And I'm like, 'cause
I'm living it.

00:39:00.960 --> 00:39:03.300
And then when she started
running a company later

00:39:03.300 --> 00:39:06.720
in her life, in her 60s,
and still today at 76,

00:39:06.720 --> 00:39:09.120
she calls me every
day and says, now

00:39:09.120 --> 00:39:12.120
I know you're talking about.

00:39:12.120 --> 00:39:15.810
That's the extent of what I
can say about my last 11 years.

00:39:15.810 --> 00:39:18.540
But please know
that I have always

00:39:18.540 --> 00:39:20.156
been an advocate for women.

00:39:20.156 --> 00:39:22.530
GABE SHERMAN: Well, and you
mentioned just on that point,

00:39:22.530 --> 00:39:24.405
on Twitter, I think,
recently I saw you said,

00:39:24.405 --> 00:39:27.300
you don't know what
my parameters were.

00:39:27.300 --> 00:39:29.370
So I guess that was
