00:39:33.304 --> 00:39:34.470
GRETCHEN CARLSON: Thank you.

00:39:34.470 --> 00:39:35.730
You can say that.

00:39:35.730 --> 00:39:38.009
Thank you.

00:39:38.009 --> 00:39:38.550
AUDIENCE: Hi.

00:39:38.550 --> 00:39:39.925
Thank you so much
