00:40:54.780 --> 00:40:56.700
I don't know, there's
something in our society

00:40:56.700 --> 00:40:59.910
that doesn't allow
us yet to honor

00:40:59.910 --> 00:41:03.000
a woman who happens to
be attractive, smart,

00:41:03.000 --> 00:41:03.750
and talented.

00:41:03.750 --> 00:41:05.791
There must be something
wrong with her, you know?

00:41:05.791 --> 00:41:09.662
So we focus, then,
on the looks first.

00:41:09.662 --> 00:41:11.370
Now I'm going to be
the first to tell you

00:41:11.370 --> 00:41:14.400
that I think media
plays into that.

00:41:14.400 --> 00:41:17.130
I don't really
watch TV that much.

00:41:17.130 --> 00:41:19.002
I just really have
been a news junkie.

00:41:19.002 --> 00:41:20.460
And over the last
couple of months,

00:41:20.460 --> 00:41:22.920
when I turn on
prime time TV, I'm

00:41:22.920 --> 00:41:25.830
horrified that my kids might
be watching this stuff,

00:41:25.830 --> 00:41:27.580
and the sexualization of women.

00:41:27.580 --> 00:41:30.540
So I think that's
where it comes from.

00:41:30.540 --> 00:41:33.810
And as parents, I don't know
how we completely control that.

00:41:33.810 --> 00:41:36.490
You can control it in your house
as much as you possibly can,

00:41:36.490 --> 00:41:40.290
but they go to school and they
do live in the outside world.

00:41:40.290 --> 00:41:43.140
And are we really going to
be able to change the imagery

00:41:43.140 --> 00:41:46.830
that we're putting out to our
kids, not to mention porn?

00:41:46.830 --> 00:41:50.400
So to me, the way to
really try to combat that

00:41:50.400 --> 00:41:53.400
is to raise our
sons differently.

00:41:53.400 --> 00:41:54.910
I come back to that point.

00:41:54.910 --> 00:41:56.640
GABE SHERMAN: And
I just want to jump

00:41:56.640 --> 00:41:59.070
in on that, because I
notice in a lot of the news

00:41:59.070 --> 00:42:02.760
