forward and say, oh,

00:42:04.750 --> 00:42:06.300
for my daughter I'm
going to do this.

00:42:06.300 --> 00:42:09.420
And as a father
of a new daughter,

00:42:09.420 --> 00:42:10.800
I know the intention is there.

00:42:10.800 --> 00:42:14.190
But to me, I also find that
language diminishing of women,

00:42:14.190 --> 00:42:17.870
because it shouldn't
just be for daughters.

00:42:17.870 --> 00:42:18.946
They're equal to men.

00:42:18.946 --> 00:42:20.070
It should be a human issue.

00:42:20.070 --> 00:42:22.950
And whether you have
a son or a daughter,

00:42:22.950 --> 00:42:27.450
I want to raise my
children to be respectful.

00:42:27.450 --> 00:42:30.270
And I'm not speaking out, or
I don't report on this issue

00:42:30.270 --> 00:42:32.060
because I have a daughter.

00:42:32.060 --> 00:42:33.060
GRETCHEN CARLSON: Right.

00:42:33.060 --> 00:42:35.724
I mean, I will give
cred to the men who

00:42:35.724 --> 00:42:37.890
stop me on the streets of
New York and shake my hand

00:42:37.890 --> 00:42:40.180
and do say thank you
for my daughters.

00:42:40.180 --> 00:42:42.824
I think it hits home
for fathers more

00:42:42.824 --> 00:42:45.490
when they hear these stories and
they do have daughters at home.

00:42:45.490 --> 00:42:47.880
And if that ignites them
to be part of this "Be

00:42:47.880 --> 00:42:49.710
Fierce" movement, fantastic.

00:42:49.710 --> 00:42:51.240
But you're exactly right.

00:42:51.240 --> 00:42:54.430
I have often said I
worked more for my son

00:42:54.430 --> 00:42:56.830
than I did for my daughter.

00:42:56.830 --> 00:42:59.260
And what I meant
by that was that I

00:42:59.260 --> 00:43:02.630
wanted him to see
what I did every day

00:43:02.630 --> 00:43:04.690
and respect his eventual
female colleagues

00:43:04.690 --> 00:43:08.260
in the workplace in the same way
in which he looked at his mom.

00:43:08.260 --> 00:43:12.760
So I do agree that the
parity is essential.

00:43:12.760 --> 00:43:15.790
And actually, more of the
focus should be on the sons

00:43:15.790 --> 00:43:18.130
than the daughters.

00:43:18.130 --> 00:43:20.530
