00:47:31.830 --> 00:47:34.170
want it to be secret or not.

00:47:34.170 --> 00:47:37.380
Start group discussions about
that in progressive companies

00:47:37.380 --> 00:47:40.480
that are willing to really
listen to their employees.

00:47:40.480 --> 00:47:43.740
I think that that is one
way to start, and to also

00:47:43.740 --> 00:47:46.710
look at your sexual
harassment training policies.

